title: Roaring dinosaurs return in 'horror' "Jurassic World" sequel
text:
Roaring dinosaurs return in 'horror'"Jurassic World" sequel 4:30pm BST - 02:16
Tension and suspense of original 1993 'Jurassic Park' film is back for dino fans, as second film in the 'World' trilogy deals with enviromental and animal rights issues. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
